224
00:24:22,010 --> 00:24:28,715
We are operating as we have been and will continue to do and we will grow with it and we're going to grow over time.

225
00:24:29,498 --> 00:24:37,325
The real excitement of this is that we're going to have partners with us who care as much about our community as we do.

226
00:24:37,845 --> 00:24:41,368
