238
00:25:54,336 --> 00:25:56,297
And it's been very helpful, at least to me,

239
00:25:57,134 --> 00:26:07,159
when residents call and actually employees of Hallmark Health and want to know what the scoop is, I can unequivocally tell them things that I've heard you mention.

240
00:26:07,819 --> 00:26:09,340
And so that's been very helpful.

241
00:26:10,360 --> 00:26:19,424
