00:37:17,338 --> 00:37:20,559
How are you going to include the community in that discussion?

368
00:37:21,880 --> 00:37:44,570
Well, we have, uh, we've been blessed to frankly, uh, for the lifetime of the Lawrence, uh, and we brought it into the hallmark that we have a group of corporate as we call them, but they're really ambassadors, uh, some 130, uh, community, uh, folks who, uh, are very much a part of our committees.

369
00:37:44,590 --> 00:37:46,791
You know, we have, uh, our own,

370
00:37:47,261 --> 00:37:50,383
the strategic planning committees that the board of trustees has.

371
00:37:50,403 --> 00:37:54,566
It includes what I call corporators that are not trustees.

372
00:37:54,606 --> 00:37:56,347
They're not employees of the hospital.

373
00:37:56,847 --> 00:38:01,871
They are community people and uh, uh, who just like working for

374
00:38:02,401 --> 00:38:06,182
community interest, because we are still a charitable organization.

375
00:38:06,222 --> 00:38:15,404
We're a not-for-profit charitable outfit, and we lean on the community quite a bit for how we use the resources that are charitable resources.

376
00:38:16,385 --> 00:38:20,146
So we will continue to have that group of some 130

377
00:38:21,568 --> 00:38:29,474
corporators that are part of our committees, that are part of our annual meeting, part of our discussion groups that we have when we make these plans.

378
00:38:30,274 --> 00:38:32,356
And that'll be a big piece of what we do.

379
00:38:33,797 --> 00:38:41,302
When we go for the investment, what's interesting about what we've put together is one financially obligated group.

380
00:38:42,183 --> 00:38:48,067
So what that means is when we go to the market for capital money,

381
00:38:49,209 --> 00:38:52,730
That capital money comes to the parent group, Welforce.

382
00:38:53,690 --> 00:38:58,272
And we are one third of the parent group to make the decisions on how to spend the money.

383
00:38:58,992 --> 00:39:02,153
But we will be responsible for our own operations.

384
00:39:02,733 --> 00:39:13,437
But we will be audited and looked at as one financially obligated group with Lowell, Tufts Medical Center, and ourselves.

385
00:39:14,037 --> 00:39:16,838
Now that's an advantage to us in borrowing money.

386
00:39:17,545 --> 00:39:28,818
