387
00:39:30,179 --> 00:39:36,286
And just a significant opportunity to attract

388
00:39:37,768 --> 00:39:41,390
more than we could ever attract on our own for capital investment.

389
00:39:41,410 --> 00:39:43,372
So that was an important thing for us.

390
00:39:43,452 --> 00:39:44,833
It wasn't the number one thing.

391
00:39:44,873 --> 00:39:57,141
The number one thing really is clinical integration, being able to take care of the patient base before they need to come to a hospital, while they're at a hospital situation, and after they're at a hospital situation.

392
00:39:58,301 --> 00:39:59,162
Not too long ago,

393
00:39:59,679 --> 00:40:01,539
We really were just a hospital.

394
00:40:01,779 --> 00:40:08,661
And it would be, if you were sick and wanted to come to us, we would take care of you and help you to be better and go back out.

395
00:40:09,421 --> 00:40:16,402
Now, so much of what we do, more than half of what we do, is outside the hospital structure itself.

396
00:40:16,502 --> 00:40:17,482
It's in the community.

397
00:40:17,582 --> 00:40:19,062
It's outreach into the community.

398
00:40:19,723 --> 00:40:22,363
And that's a whole different industry for us.

399
00:40:22,903 --> 00:40:25,063
But that means different investments, too.

400
00:40:25,864 --> 00:40:27,964
And by teaming up.

401
00:40:28,572 --> 00:40:36,396
with where we can be clinically integrated to fill the gaps that you have as a natural part of being a community hospital.

402
00:40:37,196 --> 00:40:44,920
As a standalone community hospital, you couldn't possibly have all the skills you need to take care of patients, pre-admission to post-discharge.

403
00:40:45,541 --> 00:40:49,123
When you're part of a larger organization, you can fill those gaps beautifully.

404
00:40:49,663 --> 00:40:50,803
And that's what we're going to do.

405
00:40:51,264 --> 00:40:57,727
It's going to be a tremendous advantage to this community to have an organization right in the community, right in the city of Medford.

406
00:40:58,114 --> 00:41:02,555
that has that breadth of talent and depth of talent.

407
00:41:02,615 --> 00:41:03,416
That's my question.

