00:43:53,636 --> 00:44:03,404
But what this Commonwealth has done, as you know, since 2006, has had the individual mandate, which supposedly the national government was going to build off of.

438
00:44:03,504 --> 00:44:05,846
It's a little different program at the national level.

439
00:44:06,227 --> 00:44:09,509
But the fact of the matter is, we still have that in Massachusetts.

