450
00:45:06,767 --> 00:45:09,087
Changes in the free care pool in 1991 and at the end of the 90s.

451
00:45:11,601 --> 00:45:15,763
different ways to fund the free care pool, different ways to take the money out.

452
00:45:17,284 --> 00:45:29,910
